Re: Learning to read japanese books?
by richvh » Mon 04.06.2009 12:56 pm 4 koma manga = 4 panel comic strips. Essentially newspaper comic strip format. (They're laid out vertically, so the panel size is less flexible than in American comic strips.)
Richard VanHoutenゆきの物語
