Re: Learning to read japanese books?
by clay » Mon 04.06.2009 1:20 pm Is it possible to find 4 koma manga not in newspapers?Absolutely. Look for ギャグ漫画 gyagu manga. I was thinking about Crayon Shinchan when I wrote that above. (for example here) I guess it isn't technically a 4 koma comic since it has more than 4 panels, but it is in the same spirit and short enough. TheJapanShop.com- Japanese language learning materialsCheckout our iPhone apps: TheJapanesePage.com/iPhone
